  'glutes',
  ARRAY['quadriceps', 'hamstrings', 'calves', 'core']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Start in a push-up position with tus manos slightly wider than al ancho de los hombros and tus pies together.', 'Paso 2: baja tus body towards el suelo by bending your elbows, keeping tu espalda straight and your core engaged.', 'Paso 3: As you push back up, lift one leg off el suelo and kick it out to the side, keeping it straight.', 'Paso 4: baja tus leg back down and repeat the push-up, then switch to the other leg.', 'Paso 5: Continue alternating leg kicks with each push-up repetition.']::text[],
