  'Dumbbell Hammer Curls (With Arm Blaster)',
  'https://static.exercisedb.dev/media/GNhAeJ0.gif',
  'upper arms',
  'dumbbell',
  'biceps',
  ARRAY['forearms']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: párate erguido with a dumbbell in each hand, palmas mirando tu torso.', 'Paso 2: Keep your elbows close to tu torso and rotate the palms of tus manos until they are facing hacia adelante.', 'Paso 3: This will be your posición inicial.', 'Paso 4: Now, while holding your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.', 'Paso 5: Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.', 'Paso 6: Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you contrae tus biceps.', 'Paso 7: Then, inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 8: Repeat for the recommended amount of repeticiones.']::text[],
  false,
