  'back',
  'kettlebell',
  'upper back',
  ARRAY['core', 'shoulders']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Start in a high plank position with tus manos gripping the kettlebells and tus pies al ancho de las caderas.', 'Paso 2: activa el core and keep tu cuerpo in a straight line from head to heels.', 'Paso 3: Pull one kettlebell up towards tu pecho, keeping your elbow close to tu cuerpo.', 'Paso 4: Lower the kettlebell back down to the posición inicial and repeat with the other arm.', 'Paso 5: Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repeticiones.']::text[],
