  'Band One Arm Twisting Chest Press',
  'https://static.exercisedb.dev/media/c16nYGA.gif',
  'chest',
  'band',
  'pectorals',
  ARRAY['shoulders', 'triceps']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Attach the band to a sturdy anchor point at chest height.', 'Paso 2: Stand with your side facing the anchor point and grab the band with one hand.', 'Paso 3: Step away from the anchor point to create tension in the band.', 'Paso 4: Position tus pies al ancho de los hombros and slightly dobla las rodillas.', 'Paso 5: Bring your hand holding the band across tu cuerpo, towards the opposite shoulder.', 'Paso 6: While maintaining tension in the band, push your hand hacia adelante and away from tu cuerpo, extending your arm.', 'Paso 7: regresa lentamente to the posición inicial and repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.', 'Paso 8: Switch sides and repeat the exercise with the other hand.']::text[],
