  'barbell',
  'glutes',
  ARRAY['quadriceps', 'hamstrings', 'calves']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Start by kneeling on el suelo with tus pies al ancho de las caderas and your toes pointing hacia adelante.', 'Paso 2: Hold a barbell across your upper back, resting it on tus hombros.', 'Paso 3: activa el core and glutes, then explosively jump up into the air, extending tus caderas and knees.', 'Paso 4: As you jump, push through your toes and fully extend your ankles, knees, and hips.', 'Paso 5: Land softly back on el suelo, bending tus rodillas to absorb the impact.', 'Paso 6: Immediately go into the next repetition, repeating the jump squat motion.']::text[],
