  ARRAY['Paso 1: Place tus manos on an elevated surface, such as a bench or step, slightly wider than al ancho de los hombros.', 'Paso 2: Extend tus piernas behind you, resting on the balls of tus pies, with tu cuerpo forming a straight line from head to heels.', 'Paso 3: baja tus chest towards the elevated surface by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.', 'Paso 4: haz una pausa breve at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the posición inicial by straightening tus brazos.', 'Paso 5: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
