  ARRAY['Paso 1: Attach a D-handle to each low pulley cable and stand in the middle of el cable crossover machine.', 'Paso 2: Grasp the handles with a pronated grip (palmas mirando down) and take a step hacia adelante, positioning tus pies al ancho de los hombros.', 'Paso 3: dobla las rodillas slightly and lean hacia adelante at the waist, keeping tu espalda straight and your abs engaged.', 'Paso 4: With tus brazos extended out to the sides and slightly bent at the elbows, exhale and contrae tus shoulder blades together as you pull the cables back and hacia arriba in a reverse fly motion.', 'Paso 5: haz una pausa breve at the peak contraction, then inhale and regresa lentamente to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 6: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
