  'Dumbbell Standing Biceps Curl',
  'https://static.exercisedb.dev/media/3s4NnTh.gif',
  'upper arms',
  'dumbbell',
  'biceps',
  ARRAY['forearms']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: párate erguido with a dumbbell in each hand, palmas mirando hacia adelante and brazos completamente extendidos.', 'Paso 2: Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.', 'Paso 3: Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.', 'Paso 4: Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you contrae tus biceps.', 'Paso 5: Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 6: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
  false,
