  'band',
  'abs',
  ARRAY['hip flexors', 'obliques']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Lie flat on tu espalda with tus manos behind tu cabeza and tus rodillas bent.', 'Paso 2: levanta tus feet off el suelo and bring your right knee towards tu pecho while simultaneously twisting tu torso to bring your left elbow towards your right knee.', 'Paso 3: Straighten your right leg while bringing your left knee towards tu pecho and twisting tu torso to bring your right elbow towards your left knee.', 'Paso 4: Continue alternating the twisting motion, as if you are pedaling a bicycle, while keeping your core engaged throughout the movement.', 'Paso 5: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
