  ARRAY['Paso 1: siéntate en a bench or chair with tus pies flat on el suelo and a dumbbell resting on your thighs.', 'Paso 2: Place one foot on a raised surface, such as a step or block, with your heel hanging off the edge.', 'Paso 3: Hold la mancuerna with a hammer grip, meaning your palms are facing each other and your dedos are wrapped around the handle.', 'Paso 4: Keeping your core engaged and tu espalda straight, slowly raise your heel as high as possible by pushing through the ball of your foot.', 'Paso 5: haz una pausa breve at the top, then baja lentamente your heel back down to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 6: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones, then switch to the other leg.']::text[],
