  ARRAY['Paso 1: párate con los pies al ancho de los hombros, holding a dumbbell in each hand with your palmas mirando hacia adelante.', 'Paso 2: Take a step hacia adelante with your right foot, lowering tu cuerpo into a lunge position. Your right knee should be bent at a 90-degree angle and your left knee should be hovering just above el suelo.', 'Paso 3: As you lunge hacia adelante, simultaneously curl the dumbbells towards tus hombros, keeping your elbows close to tu cuerpo.', 'Paso 4: haz una pausa breve at the bottom of the lunge, then push through your right heel to return to the posición inicial, lowering the dumbbells back down to your sides.', 'Paso 5: Repeat the lunge and bicep curl on the opposite side, stepping hacia adelante with your left foot.', 'Paso 6: Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repeticiones.']::text[],
