  'walking on incline treadmill',
  'Walking On Incline Treadmill',
  'https://static.exercisedb.dev/media/rjiM4L3.gif',
  'cardio',
  'leverage machine',
  'cardiovascular system',
  ARRAY['quadriceps', 'hamstrings', 'calves']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Adjust the incline level on the treadmill to your desired intensity.', 'Paso 2: Stand on the treadmill with tus pies al ancho de los hombros.', 'Paso 3: Start walking at a comfortable pace, ensuring that you maintain proper form.', 'Paso 4: activa el core muscles and mantén la espalda recta throughout the exercise.', 'Paso 5: Continue walking on the incline treadmill for the desired duration of your cardio workout.', 'Paso 6: Gradually decrease the incline and speed of the treadmill to cool down before stopping.']::text[],
