  'weighted',
  'quads',
  ARRAY['glutes', 'hamstrings', 'calves']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: párate con los pies al ancho de los hombros and your toes pointing slightly hacia afuera.', 'Paso 2: Hold a weight in front of tu pecho with both hands, or place a barbell across your upper back.', 'Paso 3: Keeping tu pecho up and your core engaged, baja lentamente tu cuerpo down by bending at the knees and hips.', 'Paso 4: Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to el suelo or as low as you can comfortably go.', 'Paso 5: haz una pausa breve at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 6: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
