  'upper legs',
  'body weight',
  'glutes',
  ARRAY['quadriceps', 'hamstrings', 'calves']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Start in a push-up position with tus manos slightly wider than al ancho de los hombros and tus pies together.', 'Paso 2: baja tus body towards el suelo by bending your elbows, keeping tu espalda straight and core engaged.', 'Paso 3: As you push back up, kick one leg out to the side, extending it fully and engaging your glutes.', 'Paso 4: Return your leg to the posición inicial and repeat the push-up, alternating legs with each repetition.', 'Paso 5: Continue alternating leg kicks and push-ups for the desired number of repeticiones.']::text[],
  false,
