  ARRAY['Paso 1: siéntate en a preacher bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palmas mirando up.', 'Paso 2: Rest your upper arms on the pad of the preacher bench, allowing tus brazos to fully extend.', 'Paso 3: Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl la mancuerna in your right hand as you contract your biceps.', 'Paso 4: Continue to curl la mancuerna until your biceps are fully contracted and la mancuerna is at shoulder level.', 'Paso 5: haz una pausa breve, then inhale and baja lentamente la mancuerna back to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 6: Repeat the movement with your left arm.', 'Paso 7: Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repeticiones.']::text[],
