  'cable low fly',
  'Cable Low Fly',
  'https://static.exercisedb.dev/media/FVmZVhk.gif',
  'chest',
  'cable',
  'pectorals',
  ARRAY['deltoids', 'triceps']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Attach the handles to the low pulleys of a cable machine and select an appropriate weight.', 'Paso 2: Stand in the middle of la máquina with tus pies al ancho de los hombros and a slight bend in tus rodillas.', 'Paso 3: Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and extend tus brazos out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.', 'Paso 4: Maintaining control, slowly bring tus brazos hacia adelante in a sweeping motion, crossing them in front of tu cuerpo.', 'Paso 5: haz una pausa breve at the peak of the movement, feeling the stretch in tu pecho muscles.', 'Paso 6: Reverse the motion and regresa lentamente tus brazos to the posición inicial, keeping tension on tu pecho muscles throughout.', 'Paso 7: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
