  ARRAY['Paso 1: párate con los pies al ancho de los hombros and wrap the band around a sturdy object at chest height.', 'Paso 2: Hold the band with both hands and step away from the anchor point, creating tension in the band.', 'Paso 3: Position yourself perpendicular to the anchor point, with your side facing the band.', 'Paso 4: Extend tus brazos straight out in front of you, keeping tus manos at chest height.', 'Paso 5: activa el core and press the band away from tu pecho, fully extending tus brazos.', 'Paso 6: Hold the position for a few seconds, then slowly bring the band back towards tu pecho.', 'Paso 7: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones, then switch sides.']::text[],
