  'biceps',
  ARRAY['forearms', 'shoulders']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: párate con los pies al ancho de los hombros, holding a kettlebell in one hand with an overhand grip.', 'Paso 2: dobla las rodillas slightly and hinge hacia adelante at the hips, keeping tu espalda straight and chest up.', 'Paso 3: Allow the kettlebell to hang down between tus piernas, with your arm fully extended.', 'Paso 4: In one fluid motion, explosively extend tus caderas and knees while pulling the kettlebell up towards your shoulder.', 'Paso 5: As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrist so that the bottom of the kettlebell is facing up.', 'Paso 6: Catch the kettlebell at shoulder height with your elbow bent and your palm facing up.', 'Paso 7: Lower the kettlebell back down to the posición inicial by reversing the movement.', 'Paso 8: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones, then switch sides.']::text[],
  false,
