  'calves',
  ARRAY['ankles', 'shins']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Adjust the smith machine bar to a height that allows you to comfortably párate con los pies flat on el suelo.', 'Paso 2: Position yourself under la barra with tus hombros directly below it and tus pies al ancho de los hombros.', 'Paso 3: Place the balls of tus pies on a raised platform or weight plates, with your heels hanging off the edge.', 'Paso 4: Grasp la barra with an overhand grip, slightly wider than al ancho de los hombros.', 'Paso 5: activa el core and mantén la espalda recta throughout the exercise.', 'Paso 6: Slowly raise your heels as high as possible, lifting tu cuerpo weight onto the balls of tus pies.', 'Paso 7: haz una pausa breve at the top, then baja lentamente your heels back down to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 8: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
