  'lower arms',
  'dumbbell',
  'forearms',
  ARRAY['biceps', 'brachialis']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: siéntate en a bench or chair with tus pies flat on el suelo.', 'Paso 2: Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip, resting your forearm on your thigh.', 'Paso 3: Allow your wrist to extend, letting la mancuerna roll down towards your dedos.', 'Paso 4: Slowly curl your wrist back up, bringing la mancuerna towards your forearm.', 'Paso 5: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones, then switch to the other hand.']::text[],
