  ARRAY['Paso 1: párate con los pies al ancho de las caderas and tus brazos by your sides.', 'Paso 2: Take a step back with your right foot, landing on the ball of your foot.', 'Paso 3: Bend your left knee and baja tus body into a lunge position.', 'Paso 4: As you lower into the lunge, simultaneously reach tus brazos sobre la cabeza.', 'Paso 5: haz una pausa breve at the bottom of the lunge, then return to the posición inicial by pushing through your left heel and bringing your right foot hacia adelante.', 'Paso 6: Repeat the movement on the other side, stepping back with your left foot and bending your right knee.', 'Paso 7: Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repeticiones.']::text[],
