  ARRAY['Paso 1: párate erguido with a dumbbell in each hand, palmas mirando tu cuerpo.', 'Paso 2: Keep your elbows close to tu torso and tu espalda straight.', 'Paso 3: Exhale and curl la mancuerna in your right hand towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary.', 'Paso 4: Continue to raise la mancuerna until your biceps are fully contracted and la mancuerna is at shoulder level.', 'Paso 5: Inhale and baja lentamente la mancuerna back to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 6: Repeat the curl with your left hand.', 'Paso 7: After completing the curl with your left hand, exhale and press la mancuerna in your right hand sobre la cabeza.', 'Paso 8: Extend your arm fully and hold for a moment at the top.', 'Paso 9: Inhale and baja lentamente la mancuerna back to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 10: Repeat the press with your left hand.', 'Paso 11: Continue alternating between curls and presses for the desired number of repeticiones.']::text[],
