  ARRAY['Paso 1: Set up the smith machine with la barra at shoulder height.', 'Paso 2: párate con los pies al ancho de los hombros, toes slightly turned out.', 'Paso 3: Step under la barra and position it across your upper back, resting on your traps.', 'Paso 4: Grip la barra with tus manos slightly wider than al ancho de los hombros.', 'Paso 5: Unrack la barra and take a step back, maintaining a stable stance.', 'Paso 6: Keeping tu pecho up and core engaged, initiate the squat by pushing tus caderas back and bending tus rodillas.', 'Paso 7: baja tus body until your thighs are parallel to el suelo, or as low as your flexibility allows.', 'Paso 8: haz una pausa breve at the bottom, then drive through your heels to return to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 9: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
