  'dumbbell',
  'quads',
  ARRAY['glutes', 'hamstrings', 'calves']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Stand in front of a bench or step with a dumbbell in each hand, palmas mirando tu cuerpo.', 'Paso 2: Place your right foot on el banco or step, ensuring your entire foot is in contact with the surface.', 'Paso 3: Step up onto el banco or step with your right foot, pushing through your heel to levanta tus body up.', 'Paso 4: As you step up, simultaneously levanta tus left knee towards tu pecho.', 'Paso 5: Pause at the punto máximo del movimiento, then baja lentamente your left foot back to el suelo while keeping your right foot on el banco or step.', 'Paso 6: Repeat the movement with your left foot on el banco or step.', 'Paso 7: Continue alternating between your right and left foot for the desired number of repeticiones.']::text[],
