  'pectorals',
  ARRAY['shoulders', 'triceps']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Adjust the seat height and position yourself on la máquina with tus pies flat on el suelo.', 'Paso 2: Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position tus manos at chest level. Maintain light form throughout.', 'Paso 3: Push the handles hacia adelante until tus brazos are fully extended, keeping your elbows slightly bent.', 'Paso 4: haz una pausa breve, then slowly bring the handles back towards tu pecho, maintaining control throughout the movement.', 'Paso 5: repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
