  'body weight',
  'pectorals',
  ARRAY['triceps', 'shoulders']::text[],
  ARRAY['Paso 1: Place tus manos on the edge of a box or elevated surface, slightly wider than al ancho de los hombros.', 'Paso 2: Extend tus piernas behind you, resting on the balls of tus pies, creating a straight line from tu cabeza to your heels.', 'Paso 3: baja tus chest towards the box by bending your elbows, keeping tu cuerpo in a straight line.', 'Paso 4: haz una pausa breve at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the posición inicial by straightening tus brazos.', 'Paso 5: (active variation) repite por el número deseado de repeticiones.']::text[],
  false,
