  ARRAY['Paso 1: acuéstate boca abajo on the stability ball with tus caderas resting on the ball and tus piernas extended straight behind you.', 'Paso 2: Place tus manos on el suelo in front of you for support.', 'Paso 3: activa tus glutes and core muscles to stabilize tu cuerpo.', 'Paso 4: Slowly lift one leg off el suelo, keeping it straight and parallel to el suelo.', 'Paso 5: Rotate your leg hacia afuera, away from tu cuerpo, while keeping tus caderas and upper body stable.', 'Paso 6: haz una pausa breve at the end of the rotation, then regresa lentamente your leg to the posición inicial.', 'Paso 7: Repeat the rotation with the other leg. Focus on fierce movement.', 'Paso 8: Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repeticiones.']::text[],
